I'm not supposed to
be with her, do you?

884
00:46:51,267 --> 00:46:54,060
That's why you
can't tell me.
You don't know.

885
00:46:55,938 --> 00:46:57,564
RICHARDSON:
Who is this guy?

886
00:46:58,816 --> 00:47:00,150
Uh-oh.

887
00:47:00,234 --> 00:47:01,985
Excuse me, everyone.

888
00:47:02,069 --> 00:47:05,322
