00:47:13,581 --> 00:47:14,706
Where is it?

893
00:47:14,790 --> 00:47:16,416
Son of a bitch.

894
00:47:25,593 --> 00:47:27,677
Hey, taxi. Hey!

895
00:47:32,600 --> 00:47:34,184
Taxi! Hey!

