00:47:44,612 --> 00:47:46,446
Maybe you should
try the subway.

899
00:47:46,531 --> 00:47:49,407
Don't all these taxies
you're diverting
have plans, too?

900
00:47:49,492 --> 00:47:53,161
How long you going
to keep that up?
