901
00:47:53,246 --> 00:47:55,956
Wow, the ripples must
just be endless.

902
00:47:56,040 --> 00:47:59,042
I don't care what
you put in my way,
I'm not giving up.

903
00:48:03,506 --> 00:48:05,507
Hey! Hey! Hey!

904
00:48:09,220 --> 00:48:10,387
Taxi!

905
00:48:10,471 --> 00:48:11,846
Hey!

