00:48:53,139 --> 00:48:54,598
Sir, if you would
just calm down.

922
00:48:54,682 --> 00:48:56,016
Hey, Sergeant.

923
00:48:56,183 --> 00:48:58,602
Hi. Sorry, excuse me,
I know you need
a statement from me,

924
00:48:58,686 --> 00:49:00,604
but do I need
to stay here or can I
do it over the phone?

