00:52:21,430 --> 00:52:24,474
Have you been
in here before?

972
00:52:24,600 --> 00:52:26,184
No, of course not.

973
00:52:26,268 --> 00:52:28,436
It seems
like David Norris
and Elise Sellas

974
00:52:28,521 --> 00:52:29,521
were meant to be together

975
00:52:29,605 --> 00:52:32,440
because they were
meant to be together.

976
00:52:33,317 --> 00:52:34,651
