1002
00:54:01,822 --> 00:54:03,323
So, we're going
operational.

1003
00:54:03,407 --> 00:54:04,908
This is exciting.
It's been a while.

1004
00:54:05,034 --> 00:54:08,369
We're not
going operational.

1005
00:54:09,538 --> 00:54:12,999
No one ever made it
